snippet.title: Prehistoric Life Puzzles for Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
This puzzle game from the creators of Dinosaur Fossil Puzzles introduces now some wild species from the old times!

Available on the Switch eshop:
https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/prehistoric-life-puzzles-switch/
